description:
Take a tour of the Mortal Realms, learning about their history, notable locations, and unique qualities, from the fiery realm of Aqshy to the savage beauty of Ghur. All the action of Warhammer Age of Sigmar takes place across these strange and terrible lands.

title: Warhammer Age of Sigmar – Introduction to the Mortal Realms
